This program is intended to help AHK coders to manage their projects and related stuff.

It is written in C#.
IT ISN'T YET FUNCTIONAL.

External components:
	- the MsgBoxCreator.MsgBox() method is taken from IronAHK (www.ironahk.net).
	- AvalonEdit from the SharpDevelop project (http://www.icsharpcode.net/OpenSource/SD/)
	- the RibbonControlsLibrary (Microsoft, http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/en/details.aspx?FamilyID=2bfc3187-74aa-4154-a670-76ef8bc2a0b4)
	
AvalonEdit is licensed under GPL (same as CC, see license.txt).
